714545f-a.title: Manhattan: 78th Street (East) - 2nd Avenue
714545f-a.text:
EEast 78th Street, north side, west from (No. 247), but not including Second Ave. Prominent building shown, is No. 201 East 78th Street, an apart
ment house at the N.E. corner of Third Ave.
